---
title: Crispy Falafel and Chicken on Jewelled Pilaf with Cilantro-Yogurt Sauce
description: Crispy falafel and hearty chicken sit atop an aromatic pilaf delicately flavoured with Moroccan spices and naturally sweetened with raisins. The tomato and spring mix side salad adds a refreshing bite!
